oupled ? 0 : 32} Workers</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-3 bg-black/30 border border-white/5 rounded-lg flex justify-between\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/40\">Isolation Type:</span>\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{isWarning ? \"HSM Enclave\" : \"AMD SEV-SNP\"}</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n\n          <WorkspaceCard className=\"p-5 space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <Terminal className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-widest\">eBPF Telemetry Event Streams</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"space-y-2.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-white/50 bg-black/40 border border-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl\">\n              {isDecoupled ? (\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-white/40\">\n                  <span>[23:55:00] Hardware enclave decoupled by operator.</span> <span>OK</span>\n                </div>\n              ) : (\n                <>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                    <span>[06:12:15] Context cache sync handshake initiated</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">SUCCESS</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                    <span>[06:12:16] Token count verification complete</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">VERIFIED</span>\n                  </div>\n                </>\n              )}\n            </div>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n\n          {complete && (\n            <WorkspaceCard className=\"border border-[#00FFC2]/20 bg-emerald-950/5 p-5 space-y-4 rounded-xl\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#00FFC2]/10 pb-3\">\n                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-widest\">Attestation Results</h4>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#00FFC2]/10 border border-[#00FFC2]/20 text-[#00FFC2] font-bold font-mono\">PASS</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"font-mono text-[10.5px] bg-black/50 p-4 rounded-lg text-white/60 space-y-1\">\n                <div>✔ Physical silicon registers accessed.</div>\n                <div>✔ Hardware cryptographic signature matches secure ledger.</div>\n                <div className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold text-center pt-2 uppercase\">Secure Enclave Genuine & Verified</div>\n              </div>\n            </WorkspaceCard>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n          <WorkspaceCard className=\"p-5 space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n              <Shield className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Silicon-Level Enclave Map</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"border border-white/5 bg-black/40 rounded-xl p-4 font-mono text-[9px] space-y-3\">\n              <div className=\"border border-white/10 p-2 rounded text-center bg-white/[0.01]\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/45 block uppercase text-[8px]\">HOST LAYER</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white font-medium\">Bare-Metal Sovereign Node</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"border border-[#009DFF]/30 p-2.5 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-center\">\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold block uppercase text-[8px]\">{isWarning ? \"HSM Enclave\" : \"AMD SEV-SNP\"}</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white/60 block mt-1\">Cryptographic RAM Segment</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"border border-emerald-500/30 p-2.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/5 text-center\">\n                <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold block uppercase text-[8px]\">GUEST RUNTIME</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white block mt-1 font-bold\">{agentId} Enclave</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n\n          <WorkspaceCard className=\"p-5 space-y-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#02050e] to-[#010204] border border-[#009DFF]/15\">\n            <h4 className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-widest\">Decoupled Maintenance</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n              Need physical intervention? Submit requests to GFF AI Operations Support.\n            </p>\n            <Link href=\"/portal/support\" className=\"w-full inline-flex h-8 px-4 items-center justify-center rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-mono font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider transition-all\">\n              Contact Support\n            </Link>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
